### Integration Steps

1. Configure sensor type and color mode in `isp_config_t`
2. Run calibration: dark frame (lid closed) + white reference
3. Process each scan line through `isp_process_line()`
4. Output to desired format (TIFF/JPEG/PNG/PDF)

