### Preprocessing Pipeline

For best OCR accuracy, apply these preprocessing steps:

1. Deskew — correct page rotation
2. Denoise — remove scanning artifacts
3. Binarize — convert to black/white for text
4. Rescale — ensure 300 DPI for optimal recognition

